    "body": "> create_view function after calling render\n\nI'm not sure I follow.  The `displayed` event exists to be called after a DOM widget's $el has been attached to the DOM (for things like the D3 widgets and leaflet widget).   `render` doesn't attach $el to the DOM, it just prepares it (which is why the event is needed).\n"
